overview: Alien Serve aim to provide you with simple to use services, that are low cost, high quality and most importantly reliable. We hope that we provide a solution to fulfill your requirements, whether it be a game server, voice server, dedicated server or server hardening. We have fully qualified staff available to help you with ANY issue that you may have, no matter how big or small the problem. We only use the greatest quality of hardware within our network, all our machines are running on RAID-1, so should any hard disc drive fail, most importantly there will be no downtime and no data will be lost. If you are ready to take your online experience to the next level, then you need to host with Alien Serve!
